    "description": "<h3><a name=\"Description\"></a><b>Description</b></h3>\n\n<p>Validate application behavior against expected outcomes and document test execution results for negative-path scenarios.</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3><a name=\"Activities\"></a><b>Activities</b></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Capture validation states:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Verify UI behavior for invalid inputs (e.g., error states, blocked submission)</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Capture screenshots:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Record screenshots for all failed or unexpected scenarios</li>\n\t\t<li>Include visual evidence of UI behavior (error states, modal persistence, etc.)</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Log results:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Document <b>Expected vs Actual</b> behavior for each test case</li>\n\t\t<li>Record results in test report or execution logs</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Classify outcomes:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Mark results as:\n\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t<li>Expected validation (PASS)</li>\n\t\t\t<li>Unexpected behavior (FAIL)</li>\n\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</li>\n\t\t<li>Ensure correct categorization of validation vs system errors</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3><a name=\"ExpectedOutcome\"></a><b>Expected Outcome</b></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>All test scenarios have:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Documented results</li>\n\t\t<li>Supporting screenshots (where applicable)</li>\n\t\t<li>Clear classification (pass/fail)</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Test execution is fully traceable and reviewable</li>\n</ul>\n",
